Class ManualRuleSimple

java.lang.Object
  edu.unika.aifb.foam.rules.ManualRuleSimple
All Implemented Interfaces:
Rules, java.io.Serializable
public class ManualRuleSimple
extends java.lang.Object
implements Rules

This rule set has been created by an expert ontology engineer. It contains a big set of useful rules indicating an alignment or not, 25 rules exactly. The basis are RDFS ontology constructs. The have to be combined through the ManualWeights to gain correct results. How to directly use rules for ontology alignment has been presented at WM 05.

Author:
Marc Ehrig
